thread.title: SUSAN CANO

author: SUSAN CANO
title: SUSAN CANO
text:
I submitted my prescription and it said my prescription "may" change after a year, but one month later it did not change. You called my doctor's office and they said I should come in for a visit. My eye site has not changed! I should know and I did not want to go back to the doctor's office because they just want to over charge me for their contacts!
I reordered with price smart contacts they are a couple of dollars more but well worth it.
